name: Plentiful Mineral (Primary)
desc: Purchase the Mining Charm from Master Qingxuzi to exchange the Mineral Box.
talk_pre: The treasures in Lunar Cave are abundant.  I went to the cave to collect some whenever I am free.  I have a lot of reserves.  You need to purchase the Mining Charm from me to exchange the Mineral Box.  Mineral Box is a fantastic item.  It may bring you all kinds of Mineral.  It depends on how lucky you are.
talk_accept: Let me see how lucky you are!
talk_doing: Have you ever purchased the Mining Charm from me?
talk_finish: How is it?  How lucky are you today?

name: Ancient Tree of Life
desc: Guild Leader activates the mysterious power of Ancient Tree of Life.
talk_pre: During 16:00 to 22:00 (PST) every day, Guild Leader are able to activate the mysterious power of Ancient Tree of Life.  All members can stay beside this tree to absorb essence.
talk_doing: Only 16:00 to 22:00 is available, please keep in mind!
talk_finish: Thank you for your efforts to improve the Guild.

name: Battle in Rattan Cave
desc: Finish the quest on Stone of Sword, contribute to your guild prosperity.
talk_pre: The evil force of Rattan Cave spread around Tiger Mountain.  And the trend seems to expand to Stone City. We really hope some people stand out and help us. By finishing this quest, you can earn generous reward and increase the prosperity of your guild.  Would you like to help us?
talk_accept: I have already placed the reward on the Stone of Sword,  once you finish the quest, you will get the reward automatically.
talk_finish: You are so great.  The reward are yours now.

name: Battle in Seven Stars Stage
desc: Exterminate hellions led by Golden Star Tao Guo and Mountain Man Kai.

task_failed: It's all right.  Just go there next time.
